<exploration xml:id="warm-observa-plano" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students may notice:</p>
<ul>
      <li>We can break this figure into two rectangles.</li>
      <li>Some of the side lengths are missing.</li>
      <li>We could use what we know about rectangles to find the missing side lengths.</li>
      <li>The measurements are given in feet.</li>
      <li>There is a door and windows.</li>
    </ul>
<p>Students may wonder:</p>
<ul>
      <li>What does the figure represent?</li>
      <li>What is the area of the figure?</li>
      <li>What are the missing sides?</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


